      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This enthusiast-maintained performance icon features a twin-turbocharged inline-six mated to a crisp 7-speed dual-clutch transmission. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec adaptive dampers and upgraded polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in. Power is managed via an electronically controlled limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring through the apex. Recent service includes a comprehensive fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance summer rubber. The engine exhibits strong compression and consistent boost pressure across the rev range. Minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with spirited driving, but mechanically robust and ready for the track or the canyon.",
