      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable and aesthetically pleasing drive. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor road peppering on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014standard for a car that has been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the seats are firm and the leather shows only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power features, including the sunroof and infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the brakes provide a confident, firm bite. The engine bay is tidy, showing no signs of leaks or neglect. It handles beautifully on the highway with no vibrations or pulling. Included are two sets of keys and a comprehensive folder of service records to ensure total peace of mind for the next owner.",
